  "body": "### What's your issue about?\r\nWishlist for \"next generation\" (post-release) Vyper\r\n\r\n- [x] Imports and/or package support (ethpm)\r\n  - Linking support\r\n  - Including on-chain deployed libraries\r\n- [x] Extensibility\r\n  - Struct classes\r\n  - Composable Types \"Widgets\"\r\n- [x] Improve Documatation and Examples\r\n- [x] Built-in Formal Verifier (optimize safemath gas costs, prove properties, etc)\r\n- [x] Library Support\r\n\r\n---\r\n\r\nDiscuss and create issues for above",
